    My name is Gohar Siddiqi and I am the owner of the company Best Soccer Buys Sporting Goods, Inc. based out of Atlanta. I started from our home garage and have build it to be a full time business employing great resources with an exceptional mastermind group. I used to work by myself in early stages of the business doing programming, SEO, graphics work etc. and now have a great team which shares the work.

    Company Intro

    Founded in 1999 in Atlanta Georgia USA under the name Best Soccer Buys Sporting Goods, Inc. specializing in the sports of Cricket, Field Hockey, Soccer & Squash.

    CE cricket equipment brand has grown over the years. We are a registered Cricket brand in USA and all our products are designed here in USA, manufacturing being done in different parts of the world.

    We are continuously striving to develop and distribute our top quality range of cricketing gear at highly competitive prices to our customers in United States of America. We create products which are different and unique. Our company's core values are driven by following.

    • Honesty
    • Integrity

    • Being creative and thinking out of the box
    • Enjoying what we do

    More About Our Cricket Bats

    Style Name: Blue - Painted Wood

    Comes in eye catching beautiful & multiple colours blue red and white. Light weight cricket bat for juniors’ & kids to play leisure cricket with light tennis balls. Do not used this bat with heavy tennis cricket ball. Great for Practice, Thin Razor Profile flatter on back to reduce weight

    Style Name: Reflex - Painted Wood

    Comes in eye catching beautiful & multiple colours gold yellow red & purple. Light weight cricket bat for juniors’ & kids to play leisure cricket with light tennis balls. Do not used this bat with heavy tennis cricket ball. Great for Practice, Thin Razor Profile flatter on back to reduce weight

    Style Name: Quick Silver- Fiber Glass Composite

    High Tech Composite cricket bat with awesome brute power for playing leisure cricket with light tennis balls. The bat is light weight approximately 2.4 lbs with thick profile. Great ping and drive power, water proof for playing under wet conditions.

    Style Name: Power Max - Kashmir Willow

    Unbleached Kashmir Willow bats, Grade 1. Excellent bat with strong can handle fitted with toe guard and high quality scales grip. Available in short handle, long blade and long handle sizes. This bat is available in size 6 and normal short handle full size for adults.

        How are ratings calculated?
        To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzes reviews to verify trustworthiness.
